    ATTRIBUTES   PERCENTAGE   COMMENT

    Installation:  100%    Couldn't be easier just decompress, drag and drop
    Playability:    80%    Smooth movement, but combat could be better
    Graphics:       90%    Hard to believe its not AGA in 64 color OCS mode
    Sound:          75%    A little more ambiance would help
    Documentation:  85%    A readme with all you need to play the demo
    Controls:       70%    A little too non-standard for this type of game.

@{B}Overall Score:@{UB}

83.3% This game and its engine have a definite future. Even with the few
      faults it is one of the better games of this type for the Amiga. I
      can't harp enough on the fact that it supports older OCS/ECS Amigas
      along with us AGA owners. A definate plus in my book.

