Amiga, Motorola 68020, 2mb RAM, Hard Disk, ca. 2mb free disk space, PAL
display mode, Extra Half-Brite display mode

@{B}(Recommended)@{UB}
Motorola 68030 or up, AGA chipset, Fast Memory

